# Local brand-input drop zone (source PDFs are committed in brand/source/tunera/)
brand-input/

# Promo video pipeline — intermediate website screenshots are
# regenerated on demand by `pnpm capture` (see tools/promo-video).
# The final mp4/png deliverables under public/generated/promo/ ARE
# committed because they are end-state artefacts the brand team
# consumes; only the captures folder is recomputable from the live
# dev server and stays out of git.
public/generated/promo-captures/

# Cinematic video masters drop here (image-to-video / generative
# renders, ProRes intermediates, etc). See
# docs/video/tunera-entry-cinematic-video-brief.md. Only the
# optimised web outputs under public/assets/video/ are committed.
_private/
*.mov
